[Fair comment. If fires are to help control CWD maybe their preferred site would be on deer breeding farms with good security. Thus quarantined deer could be moved to "clean" pasture while the "contaminated" pasture is burnt. And the boundary fencing is high enough to prevent the breeding deer from escaping and the wild deer to gain entry. - Mod.MHJ

